Class StackLinkedList

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.stack.AbstractStack
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.stack.StackLinkedList
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseOpsInt, ListOpsInt
public class StackLinkedList extends AbstractStack

Title: StackLinkedList

Description:

Stack implementation which employs the benefits of linked lists. Using linked lists allows us to point to previous nodes in the stack for easier traversal/deletion
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
